episodes.title: Escaping the Darkness: My Journey from Cult Member to Survivor
episodes.description: Welcome to TalksTasha! In this video, we have a special guest, Joyce, who will be sharing her personal experience with us. She will be explaining what a cult is and how she overcame it. At TalksTasha, I am dedicated to uploading real-life testimonials and stories surrounding faith and spirituality. So sit back and enjoy as Joyce takes us through her incredible journey. Don't forget to hit the like button and subscribe for more inspiring content. Thank you for joining us!!!
